    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"let it all go\"... that sounds almost peaceful. like everything would just stop hurting. it’s just that every single day is such a struggle to keep pretending that there's a future worth seeing. it feels like i'm just dragging this body around for no reason. do you think it's wrong to feel like i've already finished my part in this life?",
