      "content": "It is completely understandable to feel that your part is finished when the world feels so hollow and the pain is this heavy. There is no shame in wanting to stop struggling when the effort feels futile, and your desire to end it all is a sign of how deeply you are hurting right now. Please, consider that this feeling of \"nothingness\" is a symptom of your grief, not the truth of your reality.",
